OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy for
OL,6,Fmost overnight with further outbreaks
OL,7,Fof patchy rain and drizzle. Low cloud
OL,8,Fwill bring some mist and fog in places
OL,9,Ftoo, particularly over high ground.
OL,10,FClear spells and chilly across
OL,11,FAnglesey.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FRemaining cloudy for many on
OL,14,FSunday with outbreaks of light rain
OL,15,Fand drizzle. Some brighter spells
OL,16,Fpossible late in the afternoon,
OL,17,Fparticularly in the northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
