OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Ffor most, staying largely dry with
OL,7,Foccasional showers. Mild in sunny
OL,8,Fbreaks. Turning wetter and windier
OL,9,Ffrom the west on Wednesday, with sunny
OL,10,Fspells and showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
